Reasoning: The paper deals with graph parameters and operations on graphs, which are typical topics in discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and computational geometry (cs.CG). The study of perfect graphs and H-free graphs also falls under the category of graph theory (cs.DS). The use of complexity theory to determine the computational complexity of the problem also suggests that the paper could be classified under theoretical computer science (cs.CC).
